CatDescriptText: Portion of cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 22, 1961, pg. A13, reads: "In Concert - Among the participants in the concert celebrating the 30th anniversary of the Norris Music Club, at Stephen Foster Memorial Hall, were the above artists... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing tiered dress and eyeglasses, and man, posed in Stephen Foster Memorial Hall for concert presented by Norris Music Club
